snippet.textDisplay:
Dear Arsenal fans, your team had the chance to bury this game in the first half when there seemed to be the energy & desire but they failed to take their chance & Chelsea returned the favour in the 2nd half & took the few chances that came their way. Simple way of seeing the match really but no, instead you guys want to rant at the referee & make excuses for your team! The ref would have been right to send off players from both teams in this match & that would have resulted in a variety of outcomes including Arsenal still losses to Chelsea.

This Arsenal team lacks fitness in my opinion & on top of that they lack that toughness & fight that used to be typical of the Arsenal of years past.
